  "text": "All data are expressed as the means ± SD. The significance of the differences between two samples was determined by an unpaired Student's t-test using Microsoft Excel 2010. Differences with P < 0.05 were considered to be statistically significant. GAPDH was designed according to Tuli et al. [CITATION_1] . ITGA5 and ITGB3 were designed in our laboratory.",
